<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Happy 20th Birthday, Ate Esther!</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Lato:wght@300;400&display=swap');
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--navy:#1a2a4a;--violet:#6b4fa0;--lavender:#b39ddb;--brown:#6d4c41;--mocha:#a1887f;--cream:#fdf6ee;--gold:#c9a84c;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;background:var(--navy);color:var(--cream);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
#stars-canvas,#confetti-canvas{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
#confetti-canvas{z-index:100}
section{position:relative;z-index:1}

/* GATE */
#gate{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:999;background:var(--navy);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:2rem;padding:2rem;text-align:center;transition:opacity 0.8s ease,transform 0.8s ease}
#gate.hide{opacity:0;transform:scale(1.06);pointer-events:none}
.gate-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.2rem,4vw,1.8rem);color:var(--lavender)}
.gate-question{font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mocha)}
.gate-choices{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem;width:100%;max-width:300px}
.gate-btn{background:transparent;border:1.5px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.3);color:var(--cream);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;padding:0.85rem 1.5rem;border-radius:40px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;letter-spacing:1px}
.gate-btn:hover{border-color:var(--lavender);color:var(--lavender)}
.gate-btn.wrong{border-color:#e57373;color:#e57373;animation:shake 0.4s ease}
.gate-btn.correct{border-color:#81c784;color:#81c784;background:rgba(129,199,132,0.08)}
@keyframes shake{0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)}25%{transform:translateX(-8px)}75%{transform:translateX(8px)}}
.gate-hint{font-size:0.76rem;color:#e57373;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s;letter-spacing:1px;min-height:1rem}
.gate-hint.show{opacity:1}
.gate-lock{font-size:2.4rem;opacity:0.55}
.gdiv{width:40px;height:1px;background:rgba(179,157,219,0.25)}

/* HERO */
#hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:2rem;gap:1.5rem}
.age-badge{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(5rem,18vw,11rem);font-weight:600;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:2px var(--lavender);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-2px;opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8);transition:opacity 1s ease,transform 1s ease}
.age-badge.visible{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}
.hero-name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,5vw,3rem);color:var(--cream);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity 0.8s ease 0.3s,transform 0.8s ease 0.3s}
.hero-name.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.hero-sub{font-size:1rem;color:var(--lavender);letter-spacing:6px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:300;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.8s ease 0.6s}
.hero-sub.visible{opacity:1}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:2rem;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;color:var(--mocha);font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;animation:bounce 2s infinite}
.scroll-hint::after{content:'';width:1px;height:40px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--mocha),transparent)}
@keyframes bounce{0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(8px)}}

/* MUSIC BAR */
#music-bar{position:fixed;bottom:1.2rem;right:1.2rem;z-index:200;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;background:rgba(26,42,74,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.25);border-radius:40px;padding:0.5rem 1rem;backdrop-filter:blur(8px);opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s ease;pointer-events:none}
#music-bar.show{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.music-btn{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--lavender);font-size:1.1rem;padding:0;line-height:1;transition:transform 0.2s}
.music-btn:hover{transform:scale(1.2)}
.music-title{font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--mocha);letter-spacing:1px;white-space:nowrap}
.music-bars{display:flex;gap:2px;align-items:flex-end;height:14px}
.music-bars span{width:3px;background:var(--lavender);border-radius:2px;animation:musicbar 0.8s ease-in-out infinite}
.music-bars span:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.15s}
.music-bars span:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.3s}
.music-bars.paused span{animation-play-state:paused}
@keyframes musicbar{0%,100%{height:4px}50%{height:14px}}

/* ENVELOPE */
#envelope-section{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;gap:2rem}
.section-label{font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mocha)}
.envelope-wrap{perspective:1000px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none}
.envelope{width:min(320px,85vw);height:220px;position:relative;transform-style:preserve-3d;transition:transform 0.6s ease}
.envelope:hover{transform:rotateY(5deg) rotateX(-3deg) scale(1.03)}
.env-body{position:absolute;inset:0;background:var(--brown);border-radius:4px;border:1.5px solid var(--mocha)}
.env-flap{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:50%;background:#5d4037;clip-path:polygon(0 0,50% 60%,100% 0);border-radius:4px 4px 0 0;transition:transform 0.5s ease;transform-origin:top center}
.envelope.open .env-flap{transform:rotateX(-180deg)}
.env-lines{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-30%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.env-line{width:100px;height:2px;background:var(--mocha);border-radius:2px}
.env-seal{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--violet);border:2px solid var(--lavender);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.2rem;transition:opacity 0.3s}
.envelope.open .env-seal{opacity:0}
.open-hint{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--lavender);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;animation:pulse-text 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse-text{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.35}}
.letter-card{max-width:620px;width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.2);border-radius:12px;padding:2.5rem 2rem;display:none;opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.8s ease,transform 0.8s ease}
.letter-card.show{display:block}
.letter-card.animate{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.letter-card p{font-size:0.97rem;line-height:1.9;color:rgba(253,246,238,0.88);font-weight:300}
.letter-card p+p{margin-top:1.2rem}
.letter-verse{color:var(--lavender)!important;font-style:italic}
.letter-closing{margin-top:2rem;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--lavender);font-style:italic}

/* LIFE COUNTER */
#life-section{padding:4rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
.life-label{font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mocha)}
.life-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.1rem,3vw,1.5rem);color:var(--lavender);text-align:center}
.life-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0.8rem;max-width:520px;width:100%}
.lbox{background:rgba(107,79,160,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(107,79,160,0.28);border-radius:12px;padding:1.2rem 0.8rem;text-align:center}
.lbox-num{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,4vw,2rem);color:var(--lavender);line-height:1}
.lbox-label{font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mocha);margin-top:0.3rem}
.life-verse{font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(179,157,219,0.5);font-style:italic;text-align:center;max-width:340px}

/* WISHES */
#wishes-section{padding:5rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2.5rem}
.wishes-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,4vw,2rem);color:var(--lavender);text-align:center}
.wishes-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;max-width:680px;width:100%}
.wish-card{background:rgba(107,79,160,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(107,79,160,0.28);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity 0.5s ease,transform 0.5s ease,background 0.3s;cursor:pointer}
.wish-card:hover{background:rgba(107,79,160,0.22);transform:translateY(-3px) !important}
.wish-card.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.wish-card-inner{display:flex;align-items:stretch}
.wish-img-col{width:130px;min-width:130px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;flex-shrink:0}
.wish-img-col img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;filter:brightness(0.88) saturate(0.8);transition:filter 0.3s}
.wish-card:hover .wish-img-col img{filter:brightness(1) saturate(1)}
.img-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(107,79,160,0.45);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s}
.wish-card:hover .img-overlay{opacity:1}
.img-overlay span{font-size:0.65rem;color:white;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
.wish-text-col{padding:1.4rem 1.3rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:0.5rem}
.wish-icon{font-size:1.3rem}
.wish-prayer{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--lavender);line-height:1.4}
.wish-quote{font-size:0.76rem;color:rgba(253,246,238,0.5);font-style:italic;line-height:1.6;border-left:2px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.3);padding-left:0.7rem}

/* LIGHTBOX */
#lightbox{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:500;background:rgba(10,16,30,0.94);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1.5rem;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity 0.35s ease}
#lightbox.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.lb-inner{max-width:500px;width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;transform:scale(0.9);transition:transform 0.35s ease}
#lightbox.open .lb-inner{transform:scale(1)}
.lb-img{width:100%;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(107,79,160,0.4);max-height:340px;object-fit:contain}
.lb-prayer{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--lavender);text-align:center;line-height:1.5}
.lb-quote{font-size:0.85rem;color:rgba(253,246,238,0.6);font-style:italic;text-align:center;max-width:380px;line-height:1.7;border-top:1px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.2);padding-top:1rem}
.lb-close{background:none;border:1px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.3);color:var(--lavender);font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.6rem 1.5rem;border-radius:40px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s}
.lb-close:hover{background:var(--violet);border-color:var(--violet);color:white}
.lb-nav{display:flex;gap:1rem}
.lb-nav-btn{background:none;border:1px solid rgba(179,157,219,0.2);color:var(--mocha);font-size:1.2rem;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.lb-nav-btn:hover{border-color:var(--lavender);color:var(--lavender)}

/* CAKE */
#cake-section{padding:5rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
.cake-label{font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mocha);text-align:center}
.cake-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.2rem,3.5vw,1.6rem);color:var(--lavender);text-align:center}
#cake-canvas{cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px}
.cake-hint{font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(179,157,219,0.5);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;animation:pulse-text 2s infinite}
#cake-msg{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.1rem,3.5vw,1.5rem);color:var(--cream);text-align:center;max-width:420px;line-height:1.7;opacity:0;transition:opacity 1s ease}
#cake-msg.show{opacity:1}

/* FOOTER */
footer{padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
.footer-quote{max-width:400px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--mocha);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic}
.footer-verse{font-size:0.7rem;color:rgba(161,136,127,0.5);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
.divider{width:60px;height:1px;background:rgba(179,157,219,0.25)}

@media(max-width:480px){
  .wish-img-col{width:95px;min-width:95px}
  .wish-text-col{padding:1rem}
  .life-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
  .lbox-num{font-size:1.3rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<canvas id="stars-canvas"></canvas>
<canvas id="confetti-canvas"></canvas>
<audio id="bgMusic" loop preload="none">
  <source src="till-i-meet-you.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<!-- MUSIC BAR -->
<div id="music-bar">
  <button class="music-btn" onclick="toggleMusic()" id="musicBtn" aria-label="Play/pause music">&#9654;</button>
  <div>
    <div class="music-title">Till I Meet You &mdash; Angeline</div>
    <div class="music-bars paused" id="musicBars"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- LIGHTBOX -->
<div id="lightbox" onclick="closeLightboxOutside(event)">
  <div class="lb-inner">
    <img class="lb-img" id="lb-img" src="" alt=""/>
    <div class="lb-prayer" id="lb-prayer"></div>
    <div class="lb-quote" id="lb-quote"></div>
    <div class="lb-nav">
      <button class="lb-nav-btn" onclick="lbNav(-1)">&#8592;</button>
      <button class="lb-close" onclick="closeLightbox()">close</button>
      <button class="lb-nav-btn" onclick="lbNav(1)">&#8594;</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- GATE -->
<div id="gate">
  <div class="gate-lock">&#128274;</div>
  <div class="gate-title">Helouuuww &#x1F90D;</div>
  <div class="gdiv"></div>
  <div class="gate-question">When did we first meet?</div>
  <div class="gate-choices">
    <button class="gate-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this,false)">June 12</button>
    <button class="gate-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this,true)">July 5</button>
    <button class="gate-btn" onclick="checkAnswer(this,false)">August 20</button>
  </div>
  <div class="gate-hint" id="gateHint">Hmm, try again! Think of our special day &#x1F609;</div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="age-badge" id="ageBadge">20</div>
  <div class="hero-name" id="heroName">Happy Birthday, Ate Esther!</div>
  <div class="hero-sub" id="heroSub">A letter for your 20th year</div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- ENVELOPE -->
<section id="envelope-section">
  <div class="section-label">A message for you</div>
  <div class="envelope-wrap" onclick="openEnvelope()">
    <div class="envelope" id="envelope">
      <div class="env-body"></div>
      <div class="env-flap"></div>
      <div class="env-lines"><div class="env-line"></div><div class="env-line"></div><div class="env-line" style="width:70px"></div></div>
      <div class="env-seal">&#9993;</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="open-hint" id="openHint">tap to open</div>
  <div class="letter-card" id="letterCard">
    <p>Hwag ka muna mag-give up hahh, many years pa ang dadating sa life mo &#8212; this is just the start.</p>
    <p>I hope na you don't get stuck in that phase, na akala mo umiikot yung problems mo buong buhay mo sa kalagayan mo right now. Lilipas din yan. And may dadating pa sa life mo &#8212; tao o bagay na di mo pa nakikilala, bagong opportunity man yan o kahit bagong pagsubok pa. But whatever it will be, I am sure na anjan si Lord every step of the way.</p>
    <p>He may let you feel broken sometimes, but He will never abandon you.</p>
    <p>Just so you know &#8212; I am very proud of you. Kahit nafefeel mo man na napapalayo ka kay Lord, nakikita ko pa rin yung puso mo. Yung the fact na naalala mo pa rin si Jesus, na you still care kahit papano.</p>
    <p>I also pray that you learn to accept and embrace yourself fully, kasama na ang mga insecurities na nararamdaman mo. You are an amazing woman, atecco. You don't need to change your appearance just to please other people.</p>
    <p>Baka sa sobrang pagpapakumbaba mo, naiisip mong hindi ka karapat-dapat sa grace ni Lord. Hwag mong masyadong i-down ang sarili mo &#8212; sa paningin ni Lord, you are much more important than the sparrows. You're loved, deeply known, and highly valued by Him.</p>
    <p class="letter-verse">Matthew 10:29&#8211;31 &middot; Luke 12:6&#8211;7</p>
    <div class="letter-closing">Happy happy 20th birthday &#8212; wishing and praying for your physical and spiritual health. Enjoy your special day with Jesus! &#x1F90D;</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LIFE COUNTER -->
<section id="life-section">
  <div class="life-label">Treasure every moments</div>
  <div class="life-title">Every second is God&#39;s gift &#10022;</div>
  <div class="life-grid">
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-years">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Years</div></div>
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-months">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Months</div></div>
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-days">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Days</div></div>
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-hours">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Hours</div></div>
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-mins">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Minutes</div></div>
    <div class="lbox"><div class="lbox-num" id="lc-secs">0</div><div class="lbox-label">Seconds</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="life-verse">Fearfully and wonderfully made &mdash; Psalm 139:14</div>
</section>

<!-- PRAYERS -->
<section id="wishes-section">
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="wishes-title">Prayers for your 20s</div>
  <div class="wishes-grid" id="wishesGrid">
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(0)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F54A;&#xFE0F;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Peace that surpasses all understanding</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"Sya magbibigay saatin ng peace" &mdash; Jan 03</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(1)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F331;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Growth in faith, one step at a time</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"Kaya gusto kong maging strong sa faith" &mdash; Aug 19</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(2)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F49C;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Grace to love yourself as God loves you</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"God's love is unconditional" &mdash; Jul 26</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(3)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x2728;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Joy found in His presence, not the world</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"...your grief will turn to joy." &mdash; Aug 10</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(4)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F33F;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Healing for every wound you carry quietly</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"Healing doesnt come from running" &mdash; Aug 08</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(5)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F917;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Courage to be fully, beautifully yourself</div>
<div class="wish-quote">"Takot na takot lang talaga ako ipakita yung totoong ako" &mdash; Jul 26</div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="wish-card" onclick="openLightbox(6)">
<div class="wish-card-inner">
<div class="wish-img-col"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="message"/><div class="img-overlay"><span>tap to expand</span></div></div>
<div class="wish-text-col">
<div class="wish-icon">&#x1F64F;</div>
<div class="wish-prayer">Bold courage that goes beyond the screen</div>
